, recovered Sicily from the Arabs. His son, also called Roger, ruled Sicily as king, presiding over a court noted for its splendour and patronage of the arts."],"variants":[{"name":"Rodger","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Roger  , in part from the surname derived from the given name in the Middle Ages."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. Roger Coigniers was born in 1078, in Durham, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with Roger Coigniers II. She died in her hometown."},"et":{"1078–":"1078–Surnud","1075–1128":"1075–1128","1105–Male":"1105–Surnud","1078–Female":"1078–Surnud","1128":"1128","1105":"1105","1078":"1078","1075":"1075","Sockburne, Durham":"Durham, England","Durham, England, United Kingdom":"Durham, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1078–":"1078–Kuollut","1075–1128":"1075–1128","1105–Male":"1105–Kuollut","1078–Female":"1078–Kuollut","1128":"1128","1105":"1105","1078":"1078","1075":"1075","Sockburne, Durham":"Durham, England","Durham, England, United Kingdom":"Durham, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1078–":"1078–Décédée","1075–1128":"1075–1128","1105–Male":"1105–Décédé","1078–Female":"1078–Décédée","1128":"1128","1105":"1105","1078":"1078","1075":"1075","Sockburne, Durham":"Durham, Angleterre","Durham, England, United Kingdom":"Durham, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Roger Coigniers est née en 1078, à Durham, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Roger Coigniers II. Elle est décédée dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"1078–":"1078–Verstorben","1075–1128":"1075–1128","1105–Male":"1105–Verstorben","1078–Female":"1078–Verstorben","1128":"1128","1105":"1105","1078":"1078","1075":"1075","Sockburne, Durham":"Durham, England","Durham, England, United Kingdom":"Durham, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Roger Coigniers wurde 1078 in Durham, England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatte mit Roger Coigniers II mindestens 1 Sohn. Sie starb in ihrem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1078–":"1078–Desede","1075–1128":"1075–1128","1105–